Install MariaDB Server:
Login to the database server (ssh peter@stdb01) and install MariaDB.
sudo yum install -y mariadb-server
sudo systemctl start mariadb
sudo systemctl enable mariadb
2.Log in to MySQL as root and execute the configuration commands.
mysql -u root -p
CREATE DATABASE kodekloud_db8;
